Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.04,0:00:09.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,"NETFLIX\Nオリジナルシリーズ"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.01,0:00:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They finally bought it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.01,0:00:17.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）とうとう\N買ってもらっちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:18.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,スーパーファミコン版
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Final Fight{\i0} for the Super Nintendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:20.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“ファイナルファイト”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.02,0:00:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaguchi didn't have this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.08,0:00:23.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,矢口君が持ってなかった\Nソフトだったから...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.85,0:00:26.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）何だと！？\Nスーファミ版―
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.22,0:00:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What? You got hold of the{\i0}\N{\i1}Super Nintendo Final Fight?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.69,0:00:28.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ファイナルファイトを\N手に入れたのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.19,0:00:30.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やりに行く！　やりに行く！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.22,0:00:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let me come over and play!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.66,0:00:34.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっへへ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.66,0:00:38.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こういう事しか\N食いついてこないんだもん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.66,0:00:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only thing that'll catch\Nhis interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.17,0:00:41.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも矢口君との\N共同プレイができるのは―
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.17,0:00:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm kind of excited to play\Nco-op with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.34,0:00:42.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと嬉しいかも
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.07,0:00:44.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）何だと！？\Nスーファミ版―
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.34,0:00:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You got hold of the\NSuper Nintendo {\i1}Final Fight?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.97,0:00:46.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ファイナルファイトを\N手に入れたのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.64,0:00:48.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貸してくれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.64,0:00:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me borrow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:50.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（割れる音）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.88,0:00:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.95,0:00:51.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.75,0:00:54.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おおっ意外にケチンボだなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.81,0:00:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh. You're surprisingly stingy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.82,0:00:56.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで怒ってんの？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.05,0:00:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.45,0:00:56.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.55,0:00:59.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪〜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,ORIGINAL WORK BY RENSUKE OSHIKIRI
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:36.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,〜♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.59,0:02:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:48.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）\Nさてはお前一人で\N特訓を積むつもりだな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're planning on some solo training?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.13,0:02:49.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうよ 悪い？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.13,0:02:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Got a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:52.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まぁいいんじゃね？\Nせいぜい励むがよい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.07,0:02:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing. Train hard--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.97,0:02:54.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい 春…　あ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.97,0:02:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Haruo... Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ono!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:55.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（宮尾）大野さん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She's as mysterious and entrancing a girl\Nas always.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.14,0:03:02.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（宮尾）相変わらず妖艶(ようえん)で\N謎が多い子だよなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.25,0:03:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what she does outside of school?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:05.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,学校外では何やってんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet she has a bunch of\Nextracurricular lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:08.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱり英才教育でも\N受けているのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems to be rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:10.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イイとこのお嬢さんっぽいし
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:13.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）\Nスパ２Ｘで111連勝する\Nバケモノなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's a monster that had a 111-win streak{\i0}\N{\i1}on Super Street Fighter II Turbo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.39,0:03:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Haruo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:15.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（宮尾）なぁ 春夫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.32,0:03:19.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前同じ小学校だったんだろ\Nどんな子だったんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You both went to the same\Nelementary school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What was she like?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She was unsociable and quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:22.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）無愛想で\N無口なやつだったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.33,0:03:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:23.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（宮尾）それだけ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:24.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）それだけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I saw the two of them{\i0}\N{\i1}together in town...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:29.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）\N二人が一緒にいるのを\N街で見かけた時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it felt kind of...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:32.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだか こう…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}like the two of them{\i0}\N{\i1}were in their own world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:40.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何者をも寄せ付けない\N雰囲気を感じた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What kind of relationship did they have?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:44.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,二人の関係って\Nどんなだったんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They were still only in elementary school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:45.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,と言っても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:47.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ小学生だし...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:51.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ 考え出すと\Nモヤモヤする...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.09,0:03:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thinking about it bothers me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:52.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Back then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:55.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの時の...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:04:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That time I took your place\Nand played for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:04:00.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この前私が矢口君の代わりに\N対戦した時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.74,0:04:01.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）んん？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:03.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）隠しキャラ使って\N入ってきた人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who came in\Nusing a hidden character...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:06.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの\N大野さんって子だった気が
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.07,0:04:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like that was Ono...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.21,0:04:06.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.38,0:04:08.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（宮尾）まさか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:11.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの大野さんが\Nゲーセンでゲームするなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine Ono playing games\Nat an arcade.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:12.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,想像つかないな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you even made\Nan arcade debut, Hidaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.11,0:04:13.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:16.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日高がゲーセンデビューした\Nってのもオドロキだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:17.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）やっぱり...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:21.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くっく～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:23.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（打楽器音）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,HEAVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.56,0:04:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So the Akuma player was Ono!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:27.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,豪鬼(ごうき)使いは大野だったか...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:29.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,豪鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Akuma.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:31.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,スパ２Ｘの隠しキャラで―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.43,0:04:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A hidden character in{\i0}\N{\i1}Street Fighter II Turbo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:34.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,デモ画面で存在は\N確認していたが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.93,0:04:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew he existed from the demo sequence,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I didn't know you could use him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:36.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか使用できるとは\N知らなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:40.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,スパ２Ｘは海外の方が\N２ヶ月くらい早く―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Super Street Fighter II Turbo came out{\i0}\N{\i1}two months earlier overseas{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:42.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,稼働したらしいからな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:44.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,情報もこっちより早く\N出回ったんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so I'm sure the news made its rounds{\i0}\N{\i1}earlier over there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:47.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この業界のことに関しては―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's one pattern the industry{\i0}\N{\i1}never fails to follow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:49.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相も変わらず\N非の打ち所がねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.92,0:04:53.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 非の打ち所がねーのは\Nほとんどの事においてか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.92,0:04:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I guess some things just never fail.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna hang out at my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:55.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（女子１）私の家に\N遊びにこない？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.72,0:04:56.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（女子１）私の家に\N遊びにこない？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.72,0:04:56.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（女子２）昨日の\Nベストヒット見た？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-Did you see yesterday's "Best Hits"?\N-My aunt lives in America...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:56.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（女子２）昨日の\Nベストヒット見た？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:57.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（女子２）昨日の\Nベストヒット見た？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:57.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男子）僕の叔母さん\Nアメリカに住んでるんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:04:58.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男子）僕の叔母さん\Nアメリカに住んでるんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:05:01.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）でも なんだか\Nキュークツそうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But she looks kind of uncomfortable.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess that's the same as always, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.10,0:05:04.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そーゆーところも\N相変わらずか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:11.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男子達）おい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.34,0:05:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hey.\N-Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:12.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よっしゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:14.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イエーイ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:17.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ドリブル音）\N（歓声）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:21.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）ふふふ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:24.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,昼飯時のゲーメストは\N食が進むぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Reading Gamest magazine at lunchtime{\i0}\N{\i1}stimulates my appetite.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Astro City 29-in cabinet.{\i0}\N{\i1}250,000 yen used.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:29.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アストロシティ29インチ筐体\N中古で25万円
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:31.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とても手が出せん値段だが―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.86,0:05:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way I could afford it,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:35.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゲーメストの筐体広告は\N夢が広がるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but Gamest's cabinet advertisements{\i0}\N{\i1}are inspiring.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I could fill my room with{\i0}\N{\i1}wonderful cabinets like these,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:38.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな素晴らしい筐体で\N部屋を埋め尽くせたら
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:40.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう死んでもイイ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I would die happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.37,0:05:43.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（なみえ）ハルオ！\Nアストロシティばかりやって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruo! All you do is play Astro City!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:46.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）\N商品広告のテレカも気になる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The calling cards are interesting too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The one I really want is{\i0}\N{\i1}the Guile calling card.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:48.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっぱら欲しいのは\Nガイルテレカ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now I wanna wear the Gamest hat, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:50.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゲーメストの\Nオリジナルキャップも―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:52.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おもむろにかぶりてぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then there's the national{\i0}\N{\i1}tournament report.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:57.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして全国で行われてる\N格ゲー全国大会リポート
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:06:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got legit stats as a gamer, too.\NMakes me itch to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:06:00.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺も一端(いっぱし)の格ゲーマー\Nウズウズするぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:04.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺もいつかは\N参加してやるんだからな...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to partipate too, someday.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fighter's History Dynamite.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:12.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢ファイターズヒストリー\Nダイナマイト｣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:15.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢ワールドヒーローズ２\NＪＥＴ｣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.57,0:06:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}World Heroes 2 Jet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perfect Soldiers!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:18.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢パーフェクト\Nソルジャーズ｣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not just Street Fighter II Turbo,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:22.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,スパ２Ｘに限らず
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there are so many wonderful games{\i0}\N{\i1}waiting for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:25.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありとあらゆるゲーム達が\N俺を待っているのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll never have enough money{\i0}\N{\i1}to get them all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:28.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金がいくらあっても\N足りねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:31.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早く高校に上がってバイトが\Nできるようになりたいぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to be in high school already,{\i0}\N{\i1}so I can get a part-time job.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:32.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Ono.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:35.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ケンヂ）お…大野さんっ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for asking you here so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:37.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イキナリ呼び出して\Nゴメンよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, so, there's something I've been\Nreally wanting to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:42.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのその…　折り入って\N聞いて欲しいことがあるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone'd be watching\Nin the classroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:45.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,教室だと皆が見てるから―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.37,0:06:47.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手紙で呼び出すしか\Nなかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,so I had to resort to writing you a note.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.14,0:06:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are people watching here, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:50.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）\Nここでも見てるじゃねーか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:50.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男子Ａ）\Nケンヂ お前なら言える\N頑張れっ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:53.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男子Ａ）\Nケンヂ お前なら言える\N頑張れっ\N（男子Ｂ）\Nうぇーい！　がんばえ！\N負けるなーケンジ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-You can do it, Kenji.\N-Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-Go for it!\N-Don't fail, Kenji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:54.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男子Ａ）\Nケンヂ お前なら言える\N頑張れっ\N（男子Ｂ）\Nうぇーい！　がんばえ！\N負けるなーケンジ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:54.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:54.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男子Ａ）\Nケンヂ お前なら言える\N頑張れっ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:54.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:56.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男子Ｃ）なになに 告白？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.11,0:06:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on, a confession of love?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:57.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（女子Ａ）マジで？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:07:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't really talked much,\Nor rather, at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:06:59.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ケンヂ）まだロクに…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.51,0:07:01.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ていうか全然\N話したことないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.32,0:07:03.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,転入日の初日から
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But since the day you transferred here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.39,0:07:05.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.22,0:07:05.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男子達）おっ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.39,0:07:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It was love at first sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:07.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一目惚れです！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.59,0:07:10.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一緒に｢リトル･ブッダ｣を\N観に行きませんか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you come see the movie\N{\i1}Little Buddha {\i0}with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:10.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:17.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの表情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That expression...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:19.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメだな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.57,0:07:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I got a "no."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:20.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ケンヂ）ダメだったか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:22.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男Ｃ）ダメかー
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A no, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:24.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ケンヂ）\N見せ物じゃねぇぞこの野郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't for show, jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.97,0:07:25.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ケンヂ）くっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.01,0:07:28.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ケンヂ）やいやいお前\N四組の矢口春雄だろ！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Haruo Yaguchi from class four,\Nright?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:31.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ジロジロ見くさって\Nちきしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you sitting there staring?\NDamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:33.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いやキミが勝手に―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You just sort of started spouting\Nyour confession here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:36.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで告白劇を\N始めたんじゃないか...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:39.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前 大野さんと\Nどんな関係なんだ？　ええ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what is your relationship\Nwith Ono, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:42.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ケンヂ）\N聞けば昔 小学校が\N一緒だったらしいし...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you two went to the same\Nelementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:43.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皆信じてないけど...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No one believes it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.62,0:07:45.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大野さんとお前が\N一緒のところを―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but some people said they saw\Nyou two together!{\i1}-{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.53,0:07:47.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見たって言ってる奴が\Nいたぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.10,0:07:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What Ono means to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:49.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大野さんはお前の\Nなんなんだよぉ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:49.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大野さんはお前の\Nなんなんだよぉ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:49.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）なんなんだって\N聞かれても
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How should I know?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:51.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）なんなんだって\N聞かれても
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Someone with a shared interest?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:54.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,共通の趣味がある者同士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:57.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,といってもコイツらに\Nワケ分らんか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These guys wouldn't get it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.71,0:08:00.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大野がゲーセン好きって\Nバラすのもアレだしな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:08:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Plus it would be revealed that Ono{\i0}\N{\i1}is an arcade-lover.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:01.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大野がゲーセン好きって\Nバラすのもアレだしな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:01.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ケンヂ）\N何黙り込んでんだよぉ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just fall silent!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:01.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ケンヂ）\N何黙り込んでんだよぉ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:02.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ケンヂ）\N何黙り込んでんだよぉ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:02.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）心のライバル？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rivals?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:03.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いやいや
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, no. She just rejected a match{\i0}\N{\i1}with me the other day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:06.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つい先日コイツに対戦を\N拒否されたばかりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was even shown her true skills{\i0}\N{\i1}with that record-breaking 111 win streak.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.05,0:08:09.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかも111連勝という\N大記録で―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:11.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実力差を見せつけられた…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.52,0:08:12.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ライバルとは言えない！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not her rival.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ケンヂ）\Nさっさと\N返事しろよぉ～～！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.02,0:08:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:15.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ケンヂ）\Nさっさと\N返事しろよぉ～～！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:15.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）やはり大野は―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.92,0:08:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Would she be the person who tore{\i0}\N{\i1}my pride to shreds?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:15.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）やはり大野は―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:16.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男子Ｂ）\Nやめろよケンヂ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:17.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男子Ｂ）\Nやめろよケンヂ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:17.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）俺のプライドを\Nズタズタに引く裂く存在か？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:18.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）俺のプライドを\Nズタズタに引く裂く存在か？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:22.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だとしたら敵！？\Nというよりも
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.96,0:08:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then does that make her my enemy? Or...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.36,0:08:23.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ケンヂ）うっ　くっ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, Ono is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:25.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）俺にとって大野は…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:29.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目の上の…　たんこぶ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,a... thorn in my side?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:31.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（晶）！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:33.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぶっ ぶはははははは！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's totally what a slacker like you\Nwould say!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:35.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ケンヂ）\N劣等生が言いそうな言動だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:38.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男子Ｂ）おい！\Nこれ以上醜態を晒すな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't disgrace yourself further.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:41.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は今\Nフラれたばかりなんだぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You were just rejected, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:42.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ケンヂ）プフ～～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:43.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ケンヂ）プフ～～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:43.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男子Ａ）\Nおい 泡吹いちゃったぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, he's foaming at the mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:44.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男子Ａ）\Nおい 泡吹いちゃったぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:47.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男子Ｂ）お前がフラれた\Nばかりなんて言うから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.89,0:08:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you reminded him\Nhe was just rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.02,0:08:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ono, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.12,0:08:50.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっ 大野！\Nちょっと待て！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:52.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（足音）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ono!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:53.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）大野！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So, uh, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:57.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの なんていうか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:09:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.17,0:09:00.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）ご　ご　ごご…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:03.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,豪鬼(ごうき)の出し方\N教えてくれねぇか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.07,0:09:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering, will you show me\Nhow to use Akuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The word on the street is,\Nyou're the Akuma user.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.61,0:09:07.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,巷(ちまた)で噂(うわさ)されてる豪鬼(ごうき)使いは\Nお前だと踏んでな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:12.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うおっ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:15.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）なっ なんだよ大野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is it, Ono?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:17.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うぇっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.39,0:09:20.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（足音）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't get her...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:23.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）\Nワケがわからねぇ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.59,0:09:26.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ゲーム音）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.73,0:09:28.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）\Nお嬢様の\N言わんとしてることが―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have no idea what that little princess{\i0}\N{\i1}is trying to tell me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:29.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,検討つかねぇ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:33.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まぁ実際何も言わんのだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, she literally doesn't{\i0}\N{\i1}tell me anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ugh, it's bugging me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:35.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ ムシャクシャする！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:39.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ってなんで\Nムシャクシャしてんだ俺は
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, why am I getting riled over this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Haruo
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:40.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（宮尾）なぁ春雄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:41.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of confessing to someone\Non this Kyoto school trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.11,0:09:44.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今度の京都修学旅行でさ―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:46.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,告白してみようと思うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:47.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）誰に？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.88,0:09:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,To who?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:48.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大野さん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ono.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:51.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全然話したこともないし
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never talked to her before
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't know what kind of girl she is,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:53.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんな子なのかも\Nまるで知らないんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:56.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大野さんを見かけるたびに\N胸が熱くなるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but every time I see her, my chest burns.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:59.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（宮尾）春雄…\Nこれは恋かな？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:09:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this love, Haruo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been in love before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.23,0:10:02.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺 恋とかするの\N初めてなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It... could be that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:04.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そっそうなんじゃねぇの？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:07.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）恋に\N待ちガイルなんてねぇ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just "turtle"\Nwhen it comes to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:08.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,と思うぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.64,0:10:10.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだよな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.64,0:10:10.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（マーくん）\Nああああああああ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, there's no way I can\Nmistake my own feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:10.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（マーくん）\Nああああああああ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:14.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（マーくん）\Nああああああああ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:14.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分の気持ちを\N間違えるわけないよな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.54,0:10:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,HIDAKA SHOP
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:17.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ゲーム音）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:18.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春パパ）なーんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:20.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,スーファミ版じゃ―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess the Super Nintendo doesn't support\Nco-op play.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.38,0:10:22.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人協力プレイ\Nできなかったんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:24.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人用だね こりゃ　ワハハ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is only for solo play.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:26.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人用だね こりゃ　ワハハ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:26.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）\N己(おのれ)の無知を呪いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Curse my ignorance...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:26.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）\N己(おのれ)の無知を呪いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:30.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.13,0:10:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,JUNE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:43.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（シャッター音）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:51.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（遠野(とおの)）目的地の京都まで\Nおとなしく座ってる事...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Remain quietly in your seats until\Nwe reach our destination in Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:52.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よろしい？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:53.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（生徒全員）はーい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaguchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:55.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,矢口君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:58.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（遠野）\Nアナタ携帯ゲームなんて\N持ってきてないでしょうね？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't bring any handheld games,\Ndid you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.69,0:11:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not, Teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:11:01.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ンなわきゃねーだろがよ先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I know there's a time and place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:04.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺にだって場をわきまえる事\Nくらい出来んだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm proud of you Haruo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.86,0:11:07.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,エライぞ 春雄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing you, I thought you'd at least\Nbring a Gameboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:09.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前のことだから\Nゲームボーイの１つくらい―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:11.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,持ってくると思ったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:12.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クククッ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.43,0:11:14.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,携帯ゲームは\N持ってきてないが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't bring any handhelds,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but I did pack my TurboGrafx-16 and\Nmulti-player multi-tap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:17.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ＰＣエンジンハードと\N多人数プレイのできる―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.47,0:11:19.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マルチタップを\N持参してきたぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my dream to play {\i1}Bomberman Momotaro{\i0}\N{\i1}Dentetsu{\i0} with everyone on a hotel TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:21.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,宿泊先のテレビで皆と\N｢ボンバーマン｣や―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.98,0:11:24.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢桃太郎電鉄｣をやるのが\N夢だったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:26.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっお前って奴は…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:29.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,修学旅行の時くらい―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You could at least stop thinking about\Ngames on the school trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:31.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゲームから頭を\N離せばいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.52,0:11:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You tell him, Hidaka. Stop this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.55,0:11:33.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言ったれ言ったれ日高！\Nコイツを止めてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a once in a lifetime trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:36.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一生に一度の\N思い出なんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.62,0:11:38.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,純粋に京都を楽しもうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.62,0:11:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's enjoy Kyoto for Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.89,0:11:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoto, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.99,0:11:40.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,京都かぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, you've come.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:43.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ゲーム･ババァ）\Nよくきたのヒャヒャヒャ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:50.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ゲーム音）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:53.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）ダメだ\N｢源平討魔伝｣のせいで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Because of The Genji\Nand the Heike Clans
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.57,0:11:56.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,京都と聞くと\Nまがまがしい印象しかない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only imagine Kyoto as some\Nforeboding, evil place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.68,0:11:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing but pity\Nfor your game-brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:58.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不憫だなぁ そのゲーム脳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I was just leaving my Grandma's house,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:03.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（鬼塚(おにずか)）\Nでさー 私ばあちゃん家から\N帰ってたらさ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:06.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後ろからばあちゃんがさ\N“ちひろー！”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and Grandma comes running out, says,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.79,0:12:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"Chihiro! You forgot your underwear!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.09,0:12:06.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後ろからばあちゃんがさ\N“ちひろー！”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.09,0:12:06.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）あははは\Nなにそれ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:06.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）あははは\Nなにそれ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:08.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）あははは\Nなにそれ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:08.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“あんた\Nパンツ忘れてるよー”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:09.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“あんた\Nパンツ忘れてるよー”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:12.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とか言ってこうやって\N走ってきてさ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She came running at me yelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.13,0:12:15.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私も道の真中で\Nびっくりしちゃって
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I got freaked out in the middle\Nof the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:16.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,他にも人にいっぱい見…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.26,0:12:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All these people were watching...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:19.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（列車走行音）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:20.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ドアを開ける音）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:21.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふいー
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.70,0:12:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:23.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ドアを閉める音）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.21,0:12:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaguchi... Hey, Yaguchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.31,0:12:26.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（沼田(ぬまた)）矢口…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:29.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ…　矢口ちょっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:29.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:32.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっとスカッとするモノを\N買ってきてくれんか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.94,0:12:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you go buy something\Nrefreshing for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:34.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,サイダーとか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.38,0:12:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A soda or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:36.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）オイオイ沼田先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on now, Mr. Numada.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:39.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,新幹線に\N酔ったんじゃねーだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't get motion sickness\Nfrom a bullet train.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:41.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（沼田）どうやらそうっぽい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:43.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,新幹線で酔うなんてスゲーぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting sick from a bullet train\Nis something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.19,0:12:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty lame for a guy who looks\Nlike a master of martial arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:47.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）\N武術の達人っぽいくせに\Nだらしがねーなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We're stopped now,\Nso I'll go get it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:50.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今ちょうど停車してっから\N買ってきてやんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:53.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（沼田）スマン 自分の分も\N買っていいからな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. Buy something for yourself too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.27,0:12:54.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）ういーす
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.27,0:12:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.81,0:12:58.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yaguchi? We're about to leave.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:04.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）矢口君\Nもうすぐ出発するのに..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.48,0:13:07.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ あっとっと
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... dropped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:08.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:12.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）あーぁ もう...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:14.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,矢口君っ何やってんの？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Yaguchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.49,0:13:17.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）\Nちょうどよかった日高\Nちょっくら手伝えよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect timing, Hidaka. Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.93,0:13:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Numata asked me to buy something,\Ngave me 5000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.03,0:13:21.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）\N沼田からおつかい頼まれて\N５千円もらってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:23.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなの分も\N買ってやってんのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm buying some for everyone, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:26.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな猶予ないでしょ！\N早く戻らないと
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd better get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.27,0:13:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,True, but Numata's soda is here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:28.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）ツーてもここに\N沼田のサイダーが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:29.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）ツーてもここに\N沼田のサイダーが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:29.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（発車ベル）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:30.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（発車ベル）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:30.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（扉が閉まる音）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.77,0:13:31.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（扉が閉まる音）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.77,0:13:31.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）あ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:33.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（新幹線走行音）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:36.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（時刻表更新音）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,NEXT TRAIN DEPARTS AT...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A... A... Achoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:47.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,へっ へっ へっくしょん！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't "Achoo" me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:49.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“へっくしょん”\Nじゃないよもう！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:55.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,修学旅行初日にこんな所で\N置いてけぼりになるなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe we got left behind here\Non the first day of our school trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.26,0:13:58.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どっ どうしよう…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,F-For now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とっ とりあえず
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We should call Kyoto\Nand have someone come get us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:01.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,京都に電話して―
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:03.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰かに\N迎えに来てもらわないと
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:06.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）んまぁ\N気楽に行こーや 日高
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Just take it easy, Hidaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take a slower train or whatever,\Nas long as we get to Kyoto, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:10.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鈍行でもなんでもいいから\N京都につきゃいいんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.38,0:14:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.51,0:14:11.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Lake Biwa is close by.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:13.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,琵琶湖(びわこ)も近いし―
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:15.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,観光しながら\N京都に向かえばいいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We can head to Kyoto\Nwhile taking in the sights.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.09,0:14:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any money on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:19.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お金持ってないよ私
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:19.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（沼田）ふっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.39,0:14:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I left it all on the bullet train.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:20.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（沼田）ふっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:20.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）\N全部新幹線の中だから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.49,0:14:22.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）\N全部新幹線の中だから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.26,0:14:25.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安心しろや！\N俺はサイフ持ってるし
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.79,0:14:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got my wallet\Nand Numata's 4000 yen, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.33,0:14:26.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沼田の４千円もある！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:29.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）なっなんで\Nそんなに楽観的なの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How... can you be so carefree?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.40,0:14:30.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日高
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.46,0:14:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hidaka, you're getting worked up\N'cause you don't want to get in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:32.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は先生に\N怒られたくねーから―
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.83,0:14:33.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,焦ってんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not in elementary school anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:36.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちも\N小学生じゃねーんだから―
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.30,0:14:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We can turn this situation\Nright around on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.37,0:14:38.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな逆境バシッと\N跳ね返してやろうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.34,0:14:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Talking high and mighty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:43.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,エラそうに\N全部矢口君のせいなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all Yaguchi's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.81,0:14:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.81,0:14:48.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）うおぉおお～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,GAME CORNER
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:51.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見知らぬ土地の俺的聖域！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.88,0:14:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my sacred ground,\Nin an unfamiliar land!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:54.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）しかも誰もいねぇっ\Nこりゃたまらん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's no one here! This is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:54.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）\Nほりゃほ～わは！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I called Kyoto station and asked them\Nto inform the teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.92,0:14:58.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）\Nほりゃほ～わは！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.92,0:14:58.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）\N一応京都駅に連絡して\N伝言を頼んでおいた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:00.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おおっと！\N｢パロディウス｣だっ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:15:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's {\i1}Parodius!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The slow train is late due to\Nfalling rocks,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.43,0:15:03.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鈍行が今落石で\N遅れてるらしいから―
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:05.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しばらくここで\N立ち往生だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,so we'll have to wait here for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:07.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）これな！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.43,0:15:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This one has a character called\NChichibinta Rika.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:09.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢ちちびんたリカ｣ってのが\N出てくるんだぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:10.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢ちちびんたリカ｣ってのが\N出てくるんだぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:10.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）んぐっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, feeling aggravated?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.64,0:15:12.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっ イライラしてるな？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:14.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこのワニワニパニックで\N解消しとけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Go let off steam with that Gator Panic\Nover there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.21,0:15:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}U-Unbearable!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.98,0:15:18.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）\Nにっにくたらし～～～っ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:19.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）そうだそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.68,0:15:23.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちを置いていった皆に\N怒りの欝憤(うっぷん)をぶつけるがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat out your rage towards the ones\Nwho left us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.39,0:15:26.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）\Nアナタに怒ってんのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.39,0:15:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The rage is toward you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:28.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ゲーム機）\Nこれ！　そこのアナタ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, you over there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:29.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰だ？　俺を呼ぶのは？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:29.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アンタじゃよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.66,0:15:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's calling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:30.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと\N試していかんかね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come have a go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:31.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと\N試していかんかね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:31.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:31.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.79,0:15:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kung Fu Master, it was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.89,0:15:34.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,功夫老師\Nアンタっすか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.06,0:15:38.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,功夫老師が言う方向ボタンを\N素早く押すだけのゲームだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.06,0:15:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All you do is press the button\Nand he gives you a quick answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.90,0:15:41.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,並々ならぬ反射神経を\N要求されるのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.07,0:15:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It requires the quickest of reflexes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.24,0:15:45.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,レベル4まで行くと人間の\N限界値を超えてくるのだが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.24,0:15:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Level four exceeds the limits of humans
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:47.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺ならば楽勝だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.91,0:15:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but for me it's no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Front, ding!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.44,0:15:49.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ゲーム音）\N前ピンポン
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:50.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,左ピンポン
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Left, ding...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:51.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前ピンポン\N左ピンポン　前ピンポン
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:52.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前ピンポン\N左ピンポン　前ピンポン
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:52.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）矢口君は将来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yaguchi will probably accomplish things{\i0}\N{\i1}unrelated to academics in the future.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:53.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前ピンポン\N左ピンポン　前ピンポン
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:54.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前ピンポン\N左ピンポン　前ピンポン
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:54.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勉強とは無縁なところで\N活躍するんだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.42,0:15:54.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勉強とは無縁なところで\N活躍するんだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.48,0:15:56.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勉強とは無縁なところで\N活躍するんだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.48,0:15:56.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後ピンポン　後ピンポン\Nん　なるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hm, I see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:15:57.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後ピンポン　後ピンポン\Nん　なるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:15:59.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ドアが開く音）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.36,0:16:02.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうする？\N電車が来るまで待つ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:04.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうする？\N電車が来るまで待つ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:04.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ドアが閉まる音）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we wait for the train?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:04.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうする？\N電車が来るまで待つ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.73,0:16:08.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここでゲームして待つのも\N悪くないが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing games while we wait isn't bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but since we're here,\Nlet's go to Lake Biwa
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:10.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せっかくだから\N琵琶湖まで行くか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.23,0:16:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:11.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If we travel along Lake Biwa,\Nwe'll eventually reach Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:15.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,琵琶湖に沿っていけば\Nどうやら京都らしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:16.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:19.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな無鉄砲(むてっぽう)な行き方で\N京都を目指すの？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll aim for Kyoto with that\Nreckless travel plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If we just head there in a bus\Nor whatever,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:22.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）\Nバスでもなんでも使って\N向かってれば―
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.34,0:16:24.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのうち皆が待つ\N京都につくよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.34,0:16:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll eventually end up in Kyoto\Nwhere everyone'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:26.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）短絡的だなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very simplistic...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:34.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）\Nおおっ これが日本最大の湖\N琵琶湖の姿か！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is what the biggest lake\Nin Japan looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.02,0:16:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is a huge lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:37.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でっけー湖だなぁ～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.19,0:16:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if there are giant fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:39.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,巨大魚とかいんのかね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:40.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.36,0:16:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't have plans to see Lake Biwa\Non the school trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:44.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,修学旅行では琵琶湖に行く\Nプランが無かったから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,so don't you feel lucky, Hidaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.70,0:16:46.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,得した気分だな 日高
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:47.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）うん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.87,0:16:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:53.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）ホレ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:53.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.54,0:16:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:16:57.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）アレ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:16:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:00.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,コレってなんか…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is kind of...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.28,0:17:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,like a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:04.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,デートみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:05.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,んん？　何？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.45,0:17:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:06.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,へ！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, it's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:09.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いやいやいや\Nなんでもないの！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.02,0:17:11.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）なんだお前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.06,0:17:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did I say that out loud?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:14.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）なんで私\N口に出しちゃったの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's his relationship with Ono?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:18.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大野さんとの関係…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:21.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きっ 聞きたいな～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-I really want to ask!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.07,0:17:26.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（鳥の鳴き声）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.51,0:17:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we take a bus to the next\NTokaido Main Line station?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.57,0:17:28.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）東海道本線の\Nテキトーな駅まで―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:29.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バスで行こうか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:33.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その頃にはきっと\N電車も動いてるでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The trains should be running by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about this, Hidaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:35.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,申し訳ね～なぁ 日高
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We were on the school trip,\Nbut I dragged you into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.75,0:17:39.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せっかくの修学旅行なのに\N巻きこんじまってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:40.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,んん 別に
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I don't really mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:42.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は全然気にしてないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow, the next bus comes in 45 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.49,0:17:46.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とっ うわ\Nバスが来るのに45分後って
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:48.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）\N皆に噂とかされたらイヤだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.53,0:17:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you don't want\Npeople to start rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.03,0:17:51.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺みてーなアホに\Nつきあわされて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming along with an idiot like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:53.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっ 矢口君はどうなのよ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Being with someone like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.33,0:17:55.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私なんかと一緒で
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.54,0:18:00.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は全然…　構わないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.64,0:18:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:03.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,っていないし！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.78,0:18:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hidaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:04.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）日高～～～～～っ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:05.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Come over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:08.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっち来てみろ～～～！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,SHAVED ICE
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:15.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）何ここ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,These have vanished from our neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.59,0:18:20.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちの近所じゃとんと姿を\N見せなくなった―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.96,0:18:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A candy shop arcade!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.33,0:18:21.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,駄菓子屋ゲーセンだぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:24.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかもオレンジ筐体の数が\Nハンパねぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There are so many orange cabinets!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's {\i1}Tant-R!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:27.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）おお！\N｢タントアール｣があるぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:30.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかも新作の\N｢イチダントアール｣も！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the new{\i1} Ichidant-R!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The shop owner is obviously unmotivated,\Nbut he's got a good eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.37,0:18:34.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここの店主\Nヤル気がなさそうな割には―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:36.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目の付けどころが\Nハンパねーぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.91,0:18:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,NEED SOMETHING? RING THE BELL\N*NO EXCESSIVE RINGING
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:39.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ゲーム音）\N（春雄）そらそらぁっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.48,0:18:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There! There!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:43.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見よっ 俺のこの洞察力と\N反射神経！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.11,0:18:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold! My perceptiveness and reflexes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:45.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,へっうぃっとっ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.25,0:18:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.69,0:18:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His eyes are shining...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:47.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）あんなに眼を\Nキラキラさせて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.36,0:18:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He can have a one-track mind{\i0}\N{\i1}with his love of games...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:51.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゲーム好きで\N一方通行な面があるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but a boy who's so engrossed in something{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:53.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何かに夢中になってる\N男の子って―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:56.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,妙に魅力的なんだよな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}can be strangely appealing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:18:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hidaka, come stand to my right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:59.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日高！\Nちょっと右側来てくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:00.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）え？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:02.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,太陽が反射して見えにくい！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun glare reduces the visibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.40,0:19:04.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,っていうか\Nツープレイヤーで入ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, wanna play two-player with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.51,0:19:05.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:05.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:08.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ゲーム音）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.21,0:19:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Games are what allow me{\i0}\N{\i1}to get closest to Yaguchi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:12.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）\N矢口君と一番近くにいられる\Nきっかけがゲームなのに―
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:15.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人の間にいつも\Nはさまってるゲームの存在が
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But when they get between us{\i0}\N{\i1}when we're together,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.58,0:19:17.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっとだけ憎たらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.78,0:19:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I resent them a little.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.32,0:19:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, drinking all that juice\Njust suddenly hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.35,0:19:19.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うおお\Nジュース飲みすぎたせいか―
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.19,0:19:20.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,急にもよおしてきた！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:22.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日高！　俺の分も頼んだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hidaka, play for me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.46,0:19:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.46,0:19:23.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）えええ！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.79,0:19:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me! May I use your bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:26.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）すんませーん！\Nトイレ貸してくださーい！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.09,0:19:28.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）ああ…　なんで―
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why am I stuck with these confusing{\i0}\N{\i1}one-sided feelings?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:31.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなワケのわかんない\N片思いしてんだろ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.63,0:19:35.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（バスのエンジン音）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:38.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）うわっ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually got a winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.17,0:19:42.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たり出ちまったよー！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We walked and walked and got on a bus,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:46.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）\N歩いて歩いてバスに乗って
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,then rode the Tokaido Main Line\Nuntil finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.75,0:19:49.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,東海道本線に乗って\Nようやくか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.48,0:19:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already sundown.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:53.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう空の色もオレンジ色に\N変色してらぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:55.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）ん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.12,0:19:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's hurry and get back to everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.36,0:20:00.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）\Nさっ早く皆の所に戻って\N修学旅行を堪能(たんのう)しようや
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.73,0:20:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and enjoy the school trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.10,0:20:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably about dinner time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:02.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もうすぐ飯の時間かな？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:04.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっなんだよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.23,0:20:06.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ いや…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you worried about getting in trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.17,0:20:09.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,怒られんのが心配か？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.80,0:20:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll be the one in trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.90,0:20:12.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だ\N怒られるのは俺だし―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.71,0:20:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and Numata will vouch for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.74,0:20:14.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沼田も\Nフォローしてくれんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.64,0:20:16.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）うん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:19.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）行くベ行くべ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to be alone for a bit longer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.71,0:20:22.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）もう少し\N二人でいたかったけどなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness, even getting Hidaka involved...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:28.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（遠野）\N全く日高さんまで巻き込んで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:29.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（沼田）謝謝...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Xie xie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.92,0:20:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no big deal. We had fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.96,0:20:32.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別にいいですよ\N楽しかったから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.03,0:20:39.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男子Ｄ）\Nおおハルオ 災難だったなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.03,0:20:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Haruo, what bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:40.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男子Ｅ）\N日高と二人で―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought you snuck off\Nto fool around with Hidaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:42.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シケこんじまったかと\N思ったぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone was gossiping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.74,0:20:44.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皆噂してたぞ～～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:45.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おぉ ヒューヒュー
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.67,0:20:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Woot woot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah? Hey, wanna play {\i1}Bomberman {\i0}after?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:47.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああそう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:49.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,っていうか\Nあとでボンバーマンやろうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.71,0:20:50.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やろう！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yeah!\N-Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:51.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男子Ｅ）やるやる！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:53.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）おう お前ら！\N今日は熱い夜にしようぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make it a hot night guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:55.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男子達）よっしゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:20:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.02,0:21:01.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ゲーム音）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.99,0:21:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:02.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）おおっとぉ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,365
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.62,0:21:03.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この修学旅行は―
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.99,0:21:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This school trip is one pleasant surprise{\i0}\N{\i1}after another.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:06.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺をときめかせてくれること\Nだらけだなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:09.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ゲーム音）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:10.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）お
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:15.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アラ 大野のお嬢さん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.47,0:21:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, if it isn't Miss Ono.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.07,0:21:18.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,京都に来ても\Nゲームバカなのは―
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess even in Kyoto, you're a gamer-head\Njust like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:19.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺と変わらずか　へへっ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, it was really rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:22.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いやぁ 大変だったぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.31,0:21:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I was buying stuff when the bullet train\Ntook off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.31,0:21:25.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,買い物してたら\N新幹線が出発しちまってな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I got left behind with this girl Hidaka,\Nfrom my class.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.85,0:21:29.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日高って同じクラスの女と\N置いてきぼり食らってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.38,0:21:31.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）\N自力でコッチまで\N来たんだけど―
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.38,0:21:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We ended up getting here on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.32,0:21:33.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,道中素晴らしい\N駄菓子屋ゲーセンを―
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,On the way, I found an amazing\Ncandy shop arcade.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.35,0:21:34.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,発見したんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.36,0:21:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it would've been\Nright up your alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:36.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きっとお前も\Nグッとくる店だったぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.16,0:21:39.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや～～\N見せてやりたかったよ～～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I really wanted to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.56,0:21:44.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オー コワイ\Nなんだ怖い顔して…　ええ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.59,0:21:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.10,0:21:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the scary face?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why're you making a scary face like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:48.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな怒ったみたいな顔して\Nなんなんだ ホント
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, they've got {\i1}Gator Panic{\i0} here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:50.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おお ここにも\Nワニワニパニックがあるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.84,0:21:53.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オイ ここでちょっと\Nイライラを解消させた方が―
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't you let out some\Nfrustration with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:21:54.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいんじゃねーのか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:55.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふんっ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.21,0:21:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.28,0:21:56.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）うあっ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.08,0:21:57.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウェーイ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.11,0:21:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.18,0:21:58.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（衝撃音）\N（晶）フン！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.41,0:21:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.68,0:21:58.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（衝撃音）\N（晶）フン！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.68,0:21:58.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イテェッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.91,0:21:59.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イテェッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:01.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）なんだってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.52,0:22:04.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ワケもわからず\N怒りゲージ増やしていやがる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.75,0:22:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Her anger gauge just filled up\Nfor no reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang it! She gets on my nerves!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.02,0:22:08.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちっちくしょー\Nムシャクシャする！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.02,0:22:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just gonna have to reset myself\Nby playing{\i1} Bomberman{\i0} with everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.06,0:22:11.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こうなったら皆と\Nボンバーマンで遊んで―
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.49,0:22:13.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,リフレッシュするしかねぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.49,0:22:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.59,0:22:14.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,没収...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.56,0:22:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.63,0:22:15.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あはっ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.20,0:22:18.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪〜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.61,0:22:31.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,〜♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.25,0:22:36.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪〜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.47,0:24:02.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,〜♪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.54,0:24:12.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）\N大阪は格ゲーのメッカだ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.58,0:24:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Osaka is a fighting game mecca.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.98,0:24:15.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,噂によると\N甲子園球場の地下には―
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.01,0:24:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rumors say there's an underground arcade{\i0}\N{\i1}under the Koshien Stadium.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.32,0:24:16.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,裏世界のゲーセンがあって
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.95,0:24:18.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よなよな猛者が集まり―
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.98,0:24:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Apparently, tough players gather there{\i0}\N{\i1}to compete to be the best.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.45,0:24:20.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最強を\N競ってるらしいじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.65,0:24:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,As a true gamer, maybe I should aim\Nfor the Koshien, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.72,0:24:22.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一端のゲーマーとして―
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.36,0:24:24.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺も甲子園を\N目指してみるか！？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.13,0:24:27.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪〜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.07,0:24:34.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,〜♪
